{"tid":1065003,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(拋磚引玉)一人N條行過最難忘嘅路","createTime":"2019-03-17T03:18:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-17T03:24:40.000Z","uid":242737,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ef69b3f710dc774b762ac2102e4c3f7fe1d5ceab","tid":1065003,"uid":242737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T03:18:32.000Z","msg":"以前中學起喺寶緊山度<br />\n每次喺地鐵站行上去都好似苦行咁<br />\n不過時過境遷<br />\n回望返居然有啲懷念條長命斜<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以前曾經暗戀過一個女仔<br />\n有一排每日都經過長沙灣道<br />\n雖然而家對佢無晒感覺<br />\n但第一次陪鍾意嘅人散步係幾開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有次離家出走由九西行到九東<br />\n嗰日仲要落晒狗屎<br />\n但幾大雨都唔夠眼入面幾多水<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n歡迎大家分享吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n開心唔開心又好<br />\n香港定外國又好"},{"pid":"6d48d0310013d50bf01ee59d7c463db533a10339","tid":1065003,"uid":28451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T03:21:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5de50440b8df7a3fc881892a66cb8623bdc3b6ec","tid":1065003,"uid":229883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T03:24:40.000Z","msg":"心路歷程<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}